name: Norton Younglove Community Center
review_text: Grateful as a single mother it could get hard during the holidays thanks to a friend of mine she referred me to signed up for a toy giveaway and I sure did my kiddos were so happy I noticed they had information for the community in the wall people were a little not to nice but it's understandable it was a busy day for them

name: Norton Younglove Community Center
review_text: I'm writing this review to express my sincere gratitude to the Norton Younglove Community Center for their exceptional food programs and community-focused initiatives. The center has truly been a lifeline for me and my family. Their dedication to serving their community is truly admirable. Thank you for all that you do!

review_text: We have been working with the community center for about 4 years now. Together we have been working to bring Taekwondo to the local community.
